ent-ActionVampireToggleFangs = Toggle Fangs(Toggle)
    .desc = Extend or retract your fangs to drink blood from victims.
ent-ActionVampireGlare = Glare(Free)
    .desc = Stare down nearby targets, dealing stamina damage. Targets in front are paralyzed, muted, and take extra stamina damage over time.
ent-ActionVampireSleep = Sleep (15)
    .desc = Put target to sleep for 10 seconds
ent-ActionVampireRejuvenateI = Rejuvenate(Free)
    .desc = Instantly remove stuns and knockdown, and reset your stamina damage.
ent-ActionVampireRejuvenateII = Rejuvenate(Free)
    .desc = Remove stuns and knockdown, reset stamina, purge up to 10u of poisons, then heal 20 brute, 20 burn, 20 poison, and 25 asphyxiation over time.
ent-ActionClassSelectId = Choose Vampire Class
    .desc = Choose your vampire subclass
ent-ActionVampireHemomancerClaws = Vampiric Claws
    .desc = Create undroppable blood claws. Successful blood-draining hits grant 5 blood, the claws dissipate after 15 draining hits or when used in hand.
ent-ActionVampireSanguinePool = Sanguine Pool
    .desc = Transform into a pool of blood for 8 seconds, allowing movement through doors and windows.
ent-ActionVampireHemomancerTendrils = Blood Tendrils
    .desc = After a short delay, tendrils erupt in a 3x3 area, poisoning and heavily slowing victims.
ent-ActionVampireBloodBarrier = Blood Barrier
    .desc = Creates up to 3 blood barriers in a line at the target location. You can pass through your own barriers.
ent-ActionVampirePredatorSense = Predator Sense
    .desc = Hunt down your prey, there's nowhere to hide...
ent-ActionVampireBloodEruption = Blood Eruption(100)
    .desc = Erupt blood puddles within 10 tiles of you, dealing 50 blunt damage to targets on those puddles.
ent-ActionVampireBloodBringersRite = Blood Bringers Rite(Toggle)
    .desc = Requires full power. Toggle a 4-tile aura that costs 10 blood every 2 seconds, drains nearby victims, damages them, and heals you.
ent-ActionVampireCloakOfDarkness = Cloak of Darkness(Toggle)
    .desc = Toggle stealth that is strongest in darkness and weakest in bright light. Nearby mobs reveal you.
ent-ActionVampireShadowSnare = Shadow Snare (20)
    .desc = Place a fragile shadow trap at target location. Damages, blinds (20s) and heavily slows a non-vampire humanoid that steps on it. Trap is destroyed by flashes.
ent-ActionVampireShadowAnchor = Shadow Anchor (20)
    .desc = First use channels for 5 seconds to place a shadow anchor at your feet. Use again to return to it, or return automatically after 2 minutes.
ent-ActionVampireShadowBoxing = Shadow Boxing (50)
    .desc = Target someone to have your shadow bats beat them up. You must stay within 4 tiles for this to work.
ent-ActionVampireDarkPassage = Dark Passage (20)
    .desc = Teleport to target location through shadows.
ent-ActionVampireExtinguish = Extinguish Lights (0)
    .desc = Destroy powered lights within 4 tiles.
ent-ActionVampireEternalDarkness = Eternal Darkness (Toggle)
    .desc = When toggled, you shroud the area around you in darkness and slowly lower the body temperature of people nearby.
ent-ActionVampireEnthrall = Enthrall(150)
    .desc = Channel for 15 seconds on a humanoid target to bind them to your will. Cancels if either of you moves.
ent-ActionVampirePacify = Pacify(10)
    .desc = Flood a victim's mind with bliss, pacifying them for 40 seconds.
ent-ActionVampireSubspaceSwap = Subspace Swap(30)
    .desc = Swap positions with a living target within 7 tiles, slowing them for 4 seconds and afflicting them with hysteria for 15 seconds.
ent-ActionVampireDecoy = Decoy(30)
    .desc = Leave behind a fragile duplicate for 6 seconds and become invisible for 6 seconds. The decoy flashes attackers when harmed.
ent-ActionVampireRallyThralls = Rally Thralls(100)
    .desc = Command thralls within 7 tiles to shake off stuns, wake up, and regain stamina.
ent-ActionVampireBloodBond = Blood Bond(Toggle)
    .desc = Toggle blood tethers to visible thralls within 3 tiles, splitting incoming damage across the linked group at the cost of 2.5 blood per second.
ent-ActionVampireMassHysteria = Mass Hysteria(70)
    .desc = Requires full power. Flood nearby non-thrall humanoids within 8 tiles with terror, flashing them for 3 seconds and causing hysteria for 30 seconds.
ent-ActionVampireBloodSwell = Blood Swell(30)
    .desc = For 30 seconds, reduces brute damage by 60%, stamina and burn by 50%, halves stun times. Cannot use guns. After 400 blood, also gain +14 melee damage.
ent-ActionVampireBloodRush = Blood Rush(30)
    .desc = For 10 seconds, increase your movement speed by 50%.
ent-ActionVampireSeismicStomp = Seismic Stomp(30)
    .desc = Slam the ground, knocking down and throwing all creatures within 3 tiles away from you.
ent-ActionVampireOverwhelmingForce = Overwhelming Force(Toggle)
    .desc = Toggle - automatically pry open powered doors. While active, you cannot be shoved, body-pushed or pulled. Costs 15 blood per door.
ent-ActionVampireDemonicGrasp = Demonic Grasp(20)
    .desc = Launch a demonic hand up to 15 tiles. Immobilizes the target for 10 seconds. In combat mode, also pulls them to you.
ent-ActionVampireCharge = Charge(30)
    .desc = Requires full power. Charge in the target direction until hitting an obstacle or void. Creatures take 60 brute and are thrown 5 tiles; structures take 150 damage and walls are destroyed.
